What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Automatic Faucets Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Automatic Faucets Market

The automatic faucets market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market to reach at an estimated value of USD 955.9 million by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 7.40% in the above-mentioned forecast period.

Automatic faucets or a tap are fittings are generally equipped with sensors and advanced mechanisms helping provide a consistent flow of water by detecting the presence of hands in proximity to the water-outlet and provide hands-free operation for consumers. They halt the water flow automatically after a few seconds of operations or even if they cannot detect any presence close to the water outlet.

Focus of consumers to adopt functional products for their homes that enhance the aesthetic appeal of the household is the major factors fostering the growth of the market. Additionally, the increasing areas of application for these products due to the upgradation/modernization of bathrooms and kitchens from the end-users are also accelerating the demand for automatic faucets. However, the large levels of costs associated with the purchasing and maintenance of these products might impede the growth of market within the forecast period.

The factors such as development of automatic faucets also creates lucrative and remunerative market growth opportunities in the long run. On the flip side, the issue of counterfeit products pose as a major challenge for the market.

